  "detailed_description": "WhichWayOut? is a dark themed physics puzzle platformer.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe aim of the game is to find your way out of each level by means of abilities such as clones and light bullets.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe game will test your patience as you try to figure out what's real and what's not with limited vision and instant death awaiting failure.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe game has 20 increasing hard levels that will test the very best players.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nso there is only one question left,  can you make it out?",
